1) Install lorcon (contained in lorcon-current.tgz)  Just untar, make
and make install.

2) edit the Makefile to adjust any paths that may be different on your
system.

3) run 'make'

4) Do any necessary preparation to your card to allow it to have packets
injected to it directly.  (For atheros chipsets, use the atheros_prep.sh
script.)

5) Choose a config, and/or write one of your own

6) Run airpwn and enjoy!
